0,'wp_global_styles','',0),(1122,1,'2022-10-25 07:09:57','2022-10-07 11:43:08','','Login to Backend','','publish','closed','closed','','login-to-backend','','','2022-10-25 07:09:57','2022-10-25 07:09:57','',0,'http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/login-to-backend/',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1123,1,'2022-10-25 07:09:57','2022-10-07 11:43:08','','Legal Notice','','publish','closed','closed','','legal-notice','','','2022-10-25 07:09:57','2022-10-25 07:09:57','',0,'http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/legal-notice/',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1124,1,'2022-10-25 07:11:28','2022-10-07 11:43:08','','FU','','publish','closed','closed','','fu','','','2022-10-25 07:11:28','2022-10-25 07:11:28','',0,'http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/fu/',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1125,1,'2022-10-25 07:11:28','2022-10-07 11:43:08','','DFG','','publish','closed','closed','','dfg','','','2022-10-25 07:11:28','2022-10-25 07:11:28','',0,'http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/dfg/',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1127,1,'2023-04-24 13:23:36','2022-10-07 11:43:09','','Reference Works','','publish','closed','closed','','1127','','','2023-04-24 13:23:36','2023-04-24 13:23:36','',0,'http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1128,1,'2023-04-24 13:23:36','2022-10-07 11:43:09','','OES Applications','','publish','closed','closed','','1128','','','2023-04-24 13:23:36','2023-04-24 13:23:36','',0,'http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/',6,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1132,1,'2021-08-24 12:37:54','2021-08-24 12:37:54','<!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"oes-background-primary-color pt-5 pb-1\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group oes-background-primary-color pt-5 pb-1\"><!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"container\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group container\"><!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"66.66%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This OES Demo application is an exemplary and fictional online encyclopaedia created with the Open Encyclopedia System (OES) framework to provide users a first-hand experience of OES functionalities and features. OES is an open source framework for creating, publishing and maintaining online encyclopaedias and other works of reference in the fields of the Humanities and Social Sciences. Read more about <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"http://www.open-encyclopedia-system.org/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">Open Encyclopedia System</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The OES Demo encyclopaedia consists of an editorial layer (WordPress Plugin) to administrate and edit content, a website (WordPress Theme) to display the content and an exemplary data model including sample data. OES can be used to realise a customised online reference work. Read more: <a href=\"http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/about/about-oes-demo/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"625\">About OES Demo</a> . </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong>  The sole purpose of articles on prominent works of reference (section <em><a href=\"http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/articles/?oesf_t_demo_article_type=35\" data-type=\"t_demo_article_type\" data-id=\"18\">Articles:Reference Works</a></em>) is to provide content for the sample encylopaedia, whereas articles in the section <a href=\"http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/articles/?oesf_t_demo_article_type=32\" data-type=\"t_demo_article_type\" data-id=\"19\"><em>Articles:OES Applications</em> </a> describe current OES applications. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"33.33%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1219,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"pt-2\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full pt-2\"><img src=\"http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/oes_frontpage33-1024x871-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1219\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"container \"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1,\"className\":\"oes-content-table-header1\"} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading oes-content-table-header1\" id=\"oes-applications\">OES Applications</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Several online reference works are realised using the OES framework, ranging from online encyclopaedia to online handbook. Click on the links below to access their websites or read more about the OES applications in our exemplary <a href=\"http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/articles/?oesf_t_demo_article_type=32\" data-type=\"t_demo_article_type\">articles</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"oes-demo-card-container\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns oes-demo-card-container\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:oes/oes-card {\"oes_card_title\":\"ComDeG\",\"oes_card_body\":\"Online-Compendium der deutsch-griechischen Verflechtungen\",\"oes_card_image\":\"http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-18-at-09.55.56.png\",\"oes_card_link\":\"https://comdeg.eu/\",\"oes_card_link_text\":\"comdeg.eu\"} /--></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:oes/oes-card {\"oes_card_title\":\"Compendium heroicum\",\"oes_card_body\":\"Das Online-Lexikon des Sonderforschungsbereichs 948 „Helden – Heroisierungen – Heroismen“\",\"oes_card_image\":\"http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Screenshot-2023-01-18-at-09.56.03.png\",\"oes_card_link\":\"https://www.compendium-heroicum.de/\",\"oes_card_link_text\":\"compendium-heroicum.de\"} /--></div>