pen-encyclopedia-system.org/uber-uns/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"1143\">Über OES Demo</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Bitte beachten Sie:</strong> Die Artikel über prominente Nachschlagewerke (Abschnitt <a href=\"https://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/t_demo_article_type/reference-works/\">Artikel:Nachschlagewerk</a>) dienen ausschließlich der Bereitstellung von Inhalten für die Beispiel-Enzyklopädie, während die Artikel im Abschnitt <a href=\"https://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/t_demo_article_type/oes-application/\">Artikel:OES-Anwendung</a> aktuelle Anwendungen des OES-Frameworks beschreiben.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"33.33%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1219,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"pt-2\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full pt-2\"><img src=\"http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/oes_frontpage33-1024x871-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1219\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<p><!-- /wp:group --></p>\n<p><!-- wp:group --></p>\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"container \"} --><p></p>\n<div class=\"wp-block-group container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1,\"className\":\"oes-content-table-header1\"} --><p></p>\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading oes-content-table-header1\" id=\"oes-applications\">OES Applications</h1>\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --></p>\n<p><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\n<p>Several online reference works are realised using the OES framework, ranging from online encyclopaedia to online handbook. Click on the links below to access their websites or read more about the OES applications in our exemplary&nbsp;<a href=\"https://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/t_demo_article_type/oes-app