paedia, whereas articles in the section&nbsp;<a href=\"https://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/t_demo_article_type/oes-application/\" data-type=\"t_demo_article_type\" data-id=\"19\"><em>Articles:OES Applications</em>&nbsp;</a> describe current OES applications. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"33.33%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1219,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"pt-2\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full pt-2\"><img src=\"http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/oes_frontpage33-1024x871-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1219\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"container \"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1,\"className\":\"oes-content-table-header1\"} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading oes-content-table-header1\" id=\"oes-applications\">OES Applications</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Several online reference works are realised using the OES framework, ranging from online encyclopaedia to online handbook. Click on the links below to access their websites or read more about the OES applications in our exemplary&nbsp;<a href=\"https://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/t_demo_article_type/oes-application/\" data-type=\"t_demo_article_type\" data-id=\"19\">articles</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"oes-demo-card-container\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns oes-demo-card-container\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:oes/oes-card {\"oes_card_title\":\"ComDeG\",\"oes_card_body\":\"Online-Compendium der deutsch-griechischen Verflechtungen\",\"oes_card_image\":\"http://demo.open