raph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The OES Demo encyclopaedia consists of an editorial layer (WordPress Plugin) to administrate and edit content, a website (WordPress Theme) to display the content and an exemplary data model including sample data. OES can be used to realise a customised online reference work. Read more:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/about/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"790\">About OES Demo</a>&nbsp;.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong>&nbsp; The sole purpose of articles on prominent works of reference (section&nbsp;<em><a href=\"https://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/t_demo_article_type/reference-works/\" data-type=\"t_demo_article_type\" data-id=\"18\">Articles:Reference Works</a></em>) is to provide content for the sample encylopaedia, whereas articles in the section&nbsp;<a href=\"https://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/t_demo_article_type/oes-application/\" data-type=\"t_demo_article_type\" data-id=\"19\"><em>Articles:OES Applications</em>&nbsp;</a> describe current OES applications. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"33.33%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":1219,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"pt-2\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full pt-2\"><img src=\"http://demo.open-encyclopedia-system.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/oes_frontpage33-1024x871-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1219\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"container \"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1,\"className\":\"oes-content-table-header1\"} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading oes-content-table-header1\" id=\"oes-a